title: 328. Andy & DJ CTI: 5 Million Oil Barrels To China, Uvalde Cover-Up & Criticizing Disinformation Board
itunes:title: 328. Andy & DJ CTI: 5 Million Oil Barrels To China, Uvalde Cover-Up & Criticizing Disinformation Board
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss President Biden sending 5 million oil barrels from the US national supply overseas to China, Uvalde Mayor accusing state law enforcement of orchestrating a cover-up in the school shooting, and Nina Jankowicz stating that the GOP did a disservice to the country by criticizing the disinformation board.
